org.osmdroid.tileprovider.modules

Interface IArchiveFile

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DatabaseFileArchive, GEMFFileArchive, MBTilesFileArchive, ZipFileArchive

    public interface IArchiveFile
    The IArchiveFile is primary used to load tiles from a file archive. Generally, this should only be used for archives that require little to no computation in order to provide a given tile. For cases thereby the tiles are rendered or manipulated (such as from another projection)
    See Also:
    MapTileModuleProviderBase, ArchiveFileFactory
